  2022,"04",/general-conference/2022/04/54pace,Por Mark L. Pace,58,Correspondencia personal.
  2022,"04",/general-conference/2022/04/54pace,Por Mark L. Pace,59,Correspondencia personal.
  2022,"04",/general-conference/2022/04/54pace,Por Mark L. Pace,60,Correspondencia personal.
  2022,"04",/general-conference/2022/04/54pace,Por Mark L. Pace,61,Correspondencia personal.
